Another consideration that should be discussed is the interaction of partial
updates using XML representations with any required-ness in schema
definitions. If the designers choose to use an XML schema that defines
required elements, then the partial update may not conform to that
particular schema. There are several routes out of this situation but I
didn&#39;t see them discussed in the MS pages referenced below.


